QuestData.Title: Traces of Tampering
QuestData.Description:
So the shield has been sabotaged. Of course the ruthless Cartel Xy are the first to attempt to profit off this land.
Their greed has put us all in even more danger. We must stop them. Let us search together for signs of their passage.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find clues of Cartel Xy's presence.
